OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,FITV News' Amy Welch went to Blackpool
OL,7,Fto find out why the seaside town's
OL,8,Findustry is in danger.
OL,10,Frock makers have said they are facing
OL,11,Fa "grave and immediate challenge"
OL,12,Fafter a recent influx of cheap Chinese
OL,13,Fimports.
OL,15,FIn a letter to MPs signed by ten rock
OL,16,Fmakers from across Blackpool, Wyre &
OL,17,FFylde, they warn that the craft of
OL,18,Fcreating the rock candy is facing a
OL,19,Fcrisis like never before, and calls
OL,20,Ffor greater cultural protection to
OL,21,Fsecure the trade.
