OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,FThe resort - where almost all of the
OL,7,FUK's sticks of rock are made - has
OL,8,Fseen the number factories dwindle from
OL,9,Faround 30 to just 10 in recent years.
OL,11,FIt's feared those numbers will fall
OL,12,Ffurther as businesses face rocketing
OL,13,Fenergy costs, forcing some to reduce
OL,14,Fmanufacturing to just three or four
OL,15,Fdays a week.
OL,17,FOnly about 30 people in the UK are
OL,18,Fskilled enough to put the signature
OL,19,Flettering through the rock, with most
OL,20,Fof them living and working in
OL,21,FBlackpool.
