OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,FThe rock makers warn that "the rise of
OL,7,Fcheap Chinese imported imitations
OL,8,Fposes a grave and immediate challenge"
OL,9,Fto the industry, and are "jeopardising
OL,10,Fthe livelihoods" of Blackpool workers.
OL,12,FDespite being made in China, many of
OL,13,Fthese imported goods are still
OL,14,Flabelled as "Blackpool rock."
