OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,F"Companies have lost hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds worth of orders.
OL,8,FIt's only 3p a stick cheaper but the
OL,9,Fwholesalers are putting big orders in."
OL,11,FOver time, the sugary snack - and its
OL,12,Fassortment of colours and wording -
OL,13,Fhas become synonymous with Blackpool.
OL,15,FIn the letter to MPs, Mr Thorp went on
OL,16,Fto say: "The quality and integrity of
OL,17,FBritish confectionary is unparalleled,
OL,18,Fbuilt upon generations of
OL,19,Fcraftsmanship and expertise.
