OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,F"However, in recent months, inferior
OL,7,Fproducts have flooded our market,
OL,8,Fundercutting domestic producers and...
OL,9,Fgiving the impression to British
OL,10,Fconsumers that they are buying British
OL,11,Fproducts."
OL,13,FRock makers have now applied to the UK
OL,14,Fgeographical location as a way to stop
OL,15,Fimitations from claiming to be made in
OL,16,FBlackpool, and are calling on MPs to
OL,17,Fback their campaign.
