OL,3,CBlackpool rock 'under severe threat'
OL,4,Cfrom imported imitations
OL,6,FIf approved, only rock candy produced
OL,7,Fin or around Blackpool would be able
OL,8,Fto use the town's name on their label.
OL,9,FSuch protection already exists for
OL,10,Fproducts like Cumberland Sausages,
OL,11,FCornish pasties, and Isle of Man lamb.
